**Is your feature request related to a problem? Please describe.**
NFNet cannot be converted to onnx because of `torch.std_mean` operator.

```{python}
def get_weight(module):
 std, mean = torch.std_mean(module.weight, dim=[1, 2, 3], keepdim=True, unbiased=False) # change point
 weight = (module.weight - mean) / (std + module.eps)
 return weight
```

